{"id":327,"date":"2020-01-27T10:18:25","date_gmt":"2020-01-27T03:18:25","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/thocaca.com\/?p=327"},"modified":"2022-04-25T08:14:03","modified_gmt":"2022-04-25T01:14:03","slug":"mot-lo-tai-lieu-tieng-anh-sach","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/blog\/2020\/01\/27\/mot-lo-tai-lieu-tieng-anh-sach\/","title":{"rendered":"M\u1ed9t l\u1ed1 t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u Ti\u1ebfng Anh + S\u00c1CH"},"content":{"rendered":"\r\n<p>M\u00ecnh v\u1eeba l\u1ee5c l\u1ea1i c\u00e1i kho c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh th\u00ec t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1 t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u v\u00e0 S\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfng Anh. Ki\u1ec3u l\u00e2u l\u00e2u v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n l\u00e0 l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e0o m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00f4 s\u1ed1 t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u hay ho \u1ea5y, KAKA!<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i m\u00ecnh l\u01b0\u1ee3n nhi\u1ec1u nh\u00f3m, th\u1ea5y nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ea1n \u0111ang h\u1ecfi v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ng\u00e0nh ngh\u1ec1. C\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi m\u00ecnh th\u1ea5y m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi hay h\u1ecfi nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0:<br \/>Th\u1ee9 nh\u1ea5t, em ch\u01b0a h\u1ecdc Ti\u1ebfng Trung, l\u00ean \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc h\u1ecdc ng\u00e0nh ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef Trung \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00f4ng?<br \/>M\u00ecnh xin tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi n\u00e0y nh\u01b0 sau: M\u1ed9t n\u0103m, c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tr\u01b0\u1eddng tuy\u1ec3n sinh ng\u00e0nh ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef Trung, ho\u1eb7c ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef H\u00e0n, Nh\u1eadt,&#8230; Ch\u1ec9 ti\u00eau c\u00e1c ng\u00e0nh n\u00e0y c\u1ea3 v\u1ea1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi. Nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n th\u1eed h\u1ecfi xem kh\u1eafp Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ea5y tr\u01b0\u1eddng THPT c\u00f3 d\u1ea1y ti\u1ebfng Trung, Nh\u1eadt, H\u00e0n??? S\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u1ecdc sinh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn v\u1edbi ti\u1ebfng Trung li\u1ec7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bao nhi\u00eau so v\u1edbi con s\u1ed1 c\u1ea3 v\u1ea1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi? Cho n\u00ean l\u00e0 h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft ai c\u0169ng s\u1ebd h\u1ecdc t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u00e9. M\u1ed9t v\u00e0i b\u1ea1n t\u1ef1 h\u1ecdc tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c th\u00ec c\u0169ng d\u1ea1ng b\u1eadp b\u00f5m m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i lo v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c thua thi\u1ec7t ho\u1eb7c kh\u00f4ng theo k\u1ecbp b\u1ea1n b\u00e8 nh\u00e9! C\u00f3 m\u1ed9t l\u01b0u \u00fd nho nh\u1ecf l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecdc ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef \u1edf \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc n\u00f3 phi n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i l\u1eafm. Kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 c\u1ea5p 1, 2 h\u1ecdc c\u1ea3 k\u00ec m\u1edbi xong b\u1ea3ng ch\u1eef c\u00e1i \u0111\u00e2u. L\u00ean \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc 1 &#8211; 2 l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i c\u00e0y xong b\u1ea3ng ch\u1eef c\u00e1i r\u1ed3i \u1ea5y. Cho n\u00ean ban \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ebd th\u1ea5y b\u1ecb kh\u1edbp, ch\u00e1n ch\u00e1n. Nh\u01b0ng d\u1ea7n d\u1ea7n s\u1ebd quen th\u00f4i!<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Th\u1ee9 hai, em mu\u1ed1n h\u1ecdc song ng\u1eef th\u00ec h\u1ecdc \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u?<br \/>M\u00ecnh tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ng\u1eafn g\u1ecdn: \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef &#8211; \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Qu\u1ed1c gia H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i! Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng song ng\u1eef m\u00e0 c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 song b\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ng\u00e0nh kh\u00e1c thu\u1ed9c nh\u00f3m tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Qu\u1ed1c gia n\u1eefa c\u01a1!<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>\u0110\u1ea5y, c\u00f3 g\u00ec c\u1ee9 h\u1ecfi m\u00ecnh, c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i nhanh g\u1ecdn kh\u00f4ng. L\u00ean m\u1ea5y nh\u00f3m h\u1ecfi linh tinh r\u1ed3i to\u00e0n tin nh\u1ea3m + b\u1ecdn kh\u1ecba chuy\u1ec7n th\u00f4i \u00e0!<br \/>\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 link t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u nh\u00e9: <a href=\"https:\/\/drive.google.com\/open?id=0B6B62t1sRRFrZ092eWM2TmdxR3M\">T\u1ea0I \u0110\u00c2Y!<\/a><br \/>Ch\u00fac m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ecdc th\u1eadt t\u1ed1t nh\u00e9!<\/p>\r\n<!-- AddThis Advanced Settings generic via filter on the_content --><!-- AddThis Share Buttons generic via filter on the_content -->","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<div class=\"mh-excerpt\"><p>M\u00ecnh v\u1eeba l\u1ee5c l\u1ea1i c\u00e1i kho c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh th\u00ec t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1 t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u v\u00e0 S\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfng Anh. Ki\u1ec3u l\u00e2u l\u00e2u v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n <a class=\"mh-excerpt-more\" href=\"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/blog\/2020\/01\/27\/mot-lo-tai-lieu-tieng-anh-sach\/\" title=\"M\u1ed9t l\u1ed1 t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u Ti\u1ebfng Anh + S\u00c1CH\">[&#8230;]<\/a><!-- AddThis Advanced Settings generic via filter on get_the_excerpt --><!-- AddThis Share Buttons generic via filter on get_the_excerpt --><\/p>\n<\/div>","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":328,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[7,4,17],"tags":[102,21,32,127,19],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/327"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=327"}],"version-history":[{"count":3,"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/327\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":4235,"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/327\/revisions\/4235"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/328"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=327"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=3